main event: A UFO was observed in Memphis, Tennessee, on 05/30/52 for 25-30 seconds, with an unknown distance and flight characteristics that differed from conventional aircraft.
interesting points: The object was similar in color to, but larger than, a distant aircraft,It emitted no trail, no sound, and no light,The object's motion was unaccountable and differed from normal aircraft,The sighting occurred in broad daylight,The conclusion of the report stated it was a possible unidentified object.
witness description: Female, age 44, housewife, reported previous sightings of unusual objects in the same vicinity.
